\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the margins\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"failure\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ournew researchoffers insights on how the dark triad personality traits (narcissism, Machiavellianism and psychopathy), which tend to be more prevalent among athletes, might damage the relationship between coach and athlete, affecting their performance.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ournew\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"the dark triad personality traits\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"narcissism\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"Machiavellianism\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the relationship\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies have shown that athletes with a stronger relationship with their coachperform better.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Studies\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"that athletes\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"a stronger relationship\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"their coachperform\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1142}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elite athletes tend to be moresatisfied with their own performancewhen they have a good relationship with their coach, too.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Elite athletes\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"their own performancewhen\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"a good relationship\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"their coach\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also reporthigher levels of intrinsic motivation for sport, where they are motivated by enjoyment and excitement.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"levels\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"intrinsic motivation\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"enjoyment\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This kind of motivation is associated with increased persistence and better wellbeing.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This kind\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"motivation\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"increased persistence\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coachesandathletesalso report higher personal wellbeing when their relationship is better.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"higher personal wellbeing\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationship\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Personality traits play a powerful role in the coach-athlete relationship.\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Personality traits\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful role\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach-athlete relationship\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches and athletes aremore committed to each otherwhen they are disciplined, reliable and high in conscientiousness.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coaches\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"each otherwhen\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"conscientiousness\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 2014 studyof Chinese coach-athlete relationships found that when coaches and athletes had sociable, talkative and outgoing personality traits, it benefited their relationship.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9695503508424662, \"rank\": 0.027814063482904234, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"sociable, talkative and outgoing personality traits\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationship\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being irritable, self-conscious or anxious had a negative effect.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a negative effect\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our researchpublished in 2022 found that elite swimmers and their coaches could identify the role that their own, and their partner's personality traits played in their relationship.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elite swimmers\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"their coaches\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"their partner's personality traits\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationship\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We found actual personality traits did not seem to matter as much as an awareness of how the coach's personality affected the relationship.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"actual personality traits\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"an awareness\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach's personality\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"the relationship\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In some partnerships, the athletes valued similarities in their personalities, while others felt that their differences helped \\\"balance each other\\\".\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some partnerships\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"similarities\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"their personalities\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"their differences\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The study also found that both the coach and athlete understood that the interpersonal relationship was important for performance.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The study\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"both the coach\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2528}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the interpersonal relationship\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have recently expanded our research to explore the role of dark triad personality traits in the coach-athlete relationship.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our research\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"the role\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"dark triad personality traits\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach-athlete relationship\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These traits are often thought of negatively due to their association with being ruthless (narcissism), manipulative (Machiavellianism) or lacking empathy (psychopathy).\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These traits\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"their association\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"ruthless (narcissism\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"Machiavellianism\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"empathy\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"psychopathy\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes reporthigher levels of these traits than non-athletes.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"reporthigher levels\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"these traits\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"non\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2971}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Studies that include both athlete and coach samples tend to find they have broadly similar levels of dark triad traits.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Studies\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"both athlete\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3015}, {\"ngram\": \"coach samples\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"broadly similar levels\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"dark triad traits\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes competing in individual sports are more likely to report dark triad traits than those in team sports.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"individual sports\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"dark triad traits\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"team sports\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some studies seem to show dark triad traits may affect performance even for team sports professionals.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some studies\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"dark triad traits\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3266}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"team sports professionals\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, a 2022 UK study found basketball players high in the dark triad traitsperformed better in a free-throw taskthan those with lower levels.\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3347, \"end\": 3349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999962590815754, \"rank\": 1.8514798795485764e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball players\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"the dark triad\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"a free-throw taskthan\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"lower levels\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our new study examined how levels of these traits in both coaches and their athletes were linked to the quality of their relationship.\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our new study\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3491}, {\"ngram\": \"levels\", \"from\": 3505, \"to\": 3511}, {\"ngram\": \"these traits\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3527}, {\"ngram\": \"both coaches\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3543}, {\"ngram\": \"their athletes\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationship\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When coaches had higher narcissism, they reported less cooperative behaviour towards their athlete.\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3625}, {\"ngram\": \"higher narcissism\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"less cooperative behaviour\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"their athlete\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, they may have been less responsive to the needs of their athlete.\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3727}, {\"ngram\": \"the needs\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3776}, {\"ngram\": \"their athlete\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 3793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The relationship was better for athletes and coaches when they had different levels of narcissism - supporting the adage that \\\"opposites attract\\\".\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The relationship\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"different levels\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3879}, {\"ngram\": \"the adage\", \"from\": 3907, \"to\": 3916}, {\"ngram\": \"opposites\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athlete-coach pairs with mismatched narcissism felt closer to each other, with higher levels of trust.\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athlete-coach pairs\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3962}, {\"ngram\": \"mismatched narcissism\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3989}, {\"ngram\": \"higher levels\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4035}, {\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes high in psychopathy - associated with being ruthless - were less committed to and had less respect for their coach.\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4055}, {\"ngram\": \"psychopathy\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"less respect\", \"from\": 4142, \"to\": 4154}, {\"ngram\": \"their coach\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches high in this trait had lower levels of closeness, commitment and leadership.\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coaches\", \"from\": 4172, \"to\": 4179}, {\"ngram\": \"this trait\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4198}, {\"ngram\": \"lower levels\", \"from\": 4203, \"to\": 4215}, {\"ngram\": \"closeness\", \"from\": 4219, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"commitment\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4240}, {\"ngram\": \"leadership\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Machiavellianism was also linked with relationship quality.\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Machiavellianism\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"relationship quality\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches high in this trait - associated with manipulating and exploiting others - reported less cooperative behaviour in their relationship.\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coaches\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4325}, {\"ngram\": \"this trait\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4397}, {\"ngram\": \"less cooperative behaviour\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationship\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, athletes with high levels of Machiavellianism were less committed, felt more distant and were less willing to do their best for their coach.\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4470}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4480}, {\"ngram\": \"high levels\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4497}, {\"ngram\": \"Machiavellianism\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4517}, {\"ngram\": \"their coach\", \"from\": 4600, \"to\": 4611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our study shows that while dark triad traits may lead to higher performance in elite sports, they may undermine the quality of the relationship between coach and athlete.\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our study\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4623}, {\"ngram\": \"dark triad traits\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4658}, {\"ngram\": \"higher performance\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4689}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sports\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4705}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4737}, {\"ngram\": \"the relationship\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4771}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We only looked at this in a snapshot of time.\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a snapshot\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It may be that over time the negative aspects of these traits impede the relationships, which lead to long-term performance.\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 4956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"the negative aspects\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4877}, {\"ngram\": \"these traits\", \"from\": 4881, \"to\": 4893}, {\"ngram\": \"the relationships\", \"from\": 4901, \"to\": 4918}, {\"ngram\": \"long-term performance\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Within the study, coaches and athletes reported broadly similar levels of the dark triad traits to each other.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 